OL,5,ETHE NEXT GENERATION OF VEGANS Q j 7   Q
OL,7,BA growing number of youngsters are     
OL,8,Eavoiding beefBin the wake of the BSE or
OL,9,Bmad cow diseaseBcrisis.                
OL,11,EThe Vegetarian SocietyBclaims 38% of   
OL,12,Bfour to 11-year-olds were avoiding beef
OL,13,Bfollowing widespread concern that BSE  
OL,14,Bcould be passed from infected cattle to
OL,15,Bhumans via the food chain.             
OL,17,B"However one in five are rejecting meat
OL,18,Baltogether as a result of the scare,"  
OL,19,Bsays spokesmanESam Calvert.            
