OL,4,G````````````````````````````TRQ 5~%  Q
OL,5,ETHE NEXT GENERATION OF VEGANS Q j 7   Q
OL,7,BNew CenturionEJoanne Harrison,B15, from
OL,8,BManchester, told Eco Scene: "Since the 
OL,9,BBSE scare I haven't eaten beef. I'd    
OL,10,Blike to quit eating meat altogether but
OL,11,BI'm concerned about nutrition."        
OL,13,BVegetarian Sam Calvert said: "Many     
OL,14,Bpeople think that vegetarians and      
OL,15,Bvegans areEpale, weakBandEstarving.    
OL,17,B"But if you eatEpulses, vegetables,    
OL,18,Efruit, cerealsBandEdairy productsBdaily
OL,19,Bthat needn't be the case."             
