OL,5,ETHE NEXT GENERATION OF VEGANS Q j 7   Q
OL,7,BEco-viewerELaura McDouall,B14, from    
OL,8,BShropshire, cannot understand why so   
OL,9,Bmany people are turning vegetarian.    
OL,11,BShe reasons: "There are a lot of       
OL,12,Banimals in this world. If we didn't eat
OL,13,Bthem, theyEwouldn't serve a purposeBand
OL,14,Beventually there would be too many."   
OL,16,BVegetarianESuzannah Makin,B15, from    
OL,17,BLancashire, disagrees: "Animals are    
OL,18,Bequal to man and we have no right to   
OL,19,Bcruelly kill or eat them."             
