OL,5,ETHE NEXT GENERATION OF VEGANS Q j 7   Q
OL,7,B"Eating meat is natural to man," says  
OL,8,B15-year-old New CenturionELuke Ribbons,
OL,9,Bfrom Huddersfield. "You could say it's 
OL,10,Bequivalent to breathing because man    
OL,11,Bcannot live off leaves alone!"         
OL,13,BSam Calvert, of The Vegetarian Society,
OL,14,Breplies: "I agree thatEman cannot live 
OL,15,Eoff leaves alone.                      
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17,B"But there are manyEculturesBin the    
OL,18,Bworld who for centuries have lived     
OL,19,Bhealthily on vegetarian diets!"        
