OL,5,ETHE NEXT GENERATION OF VEGANS Q j 7   Q
OL,7,B"I used to be a vegetarian," says Eco- 
OL,8,BviewerEMichael Creek,B14, from North   
OL,9,BYorkshire. "I didn't agree with the way
OL,10,Banimals were treated and slaughtered.  
OL,12,B"However,EI got boredBwith what I was  
OL,13,Beating and so I went back to meat."    
OL,15,B"That's a common problem," says Sam    
OL,16,BCalvert from The Vegetarian Society.   
OL,17,B"So if you'd like details of tasty,    
OL,18,Bnutritious vegetarian dishes or advice 
OL,19,Bcall us onE0161 928 0793."             
